    rdfs:label "Differs from the canonical pMB1 origin (pBR322/pUC) by 2 bp at positions 412-413 in the RNA I/RNA II control region; a long-established, benign cloning-vector form present in 140+ deposited vectors since 1985, so the difference does not impair replication." ;
